        options: ["Epilepsy cannot be diagnosed until a second unprovoked seizure occurs","Epilepsy can be diagnosed now because the structural lesion and EEG findings indicate recurrence risk exceeding 60%","The patient should be observed without treatment until a second seizure occurs","An epilepsy diagnosis requires a minimum of three unprovoked seizures"],
